values:
WOW! A lot has happened since I last updated.  My brother came home today and he made a date with me....(nothing to get jealous over, i have to do his homework for school).  Work was very interesting and if you wanna know about that just ask.  Break just started and I already miss seeing all my friends.  Since it started snowing i have gotten into the Christmas mood.  I cant believe it. Ok....If you wanna know more ask. im going to bed.  see ya later today!!! If i dont see any of you know that i love you all....

Marta

Well yesterday was very intersting......I went to court and I'm not getting into that so dont even ask.  Later my parents went out so i was home alone.  me and my sister went shopping and i found black shoes...that made me happy.  we later went out to eat at taco bell and becky called me.  we went to pick her up and we hung out at my house.....when i was driving her home matt called so i went over there for a minute only to get called home.  my sister was faking being scared and i was gonna kill her.  we hung out a little and i drove everyone home.  then i sorta worked on my english project.

today was i dunno. i slept most of the day.  more work on my english project and OMG its done.  i cant wait till tomorrow is over.  anyways im going to bed.  see all of you later i hope.
well today was pretty bad...............school went by pretty fast except for roman. im really worried about that speech.  work was a lot of fun.  we had a throwing fry contest!

Today was a pretty good day....for a while at least.  School went by quick even if I didn't want to be there.  I came home to do nothing special.  We later left to drop my sister off at Polish school and we went shoe shopping......OMG I cannot believe I could not find black sketchers anywhere.  That really got me mad.  Maybe I have to settle for white ones.  If anyone knows where I can look please let me know....Anyways I'm out for tonight....
